original_font_information.description:
The pan-European Cera Collection is driven by pure geometry and contains the bestselling Cera plus Cera Condensed, its stenciled counterpart Cera Stencil, the hand-crafted display companion Cera Brush and soft Cera Round.

This is the updated version from 2018, featuring improvements on Greek and Cyrillic script plus overall Kerning updates.
